quran[8{c,v,t}:
6,1,"tareef Allah ke liye hai jis ne zameen aur aasman banaye, roshni aur tarikhiyan peda kee phir bhi woh log jinhon ne dawat haq ko maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai dosaron ko apne rab ka humsartehra rahay hain"
6,2,"wohi hai jis ne tum ko matti se peda kya, phir tumahray liye zindagi ki aik muddat muqarrar kar di, aur aik doosri muddat aur bhi hai jwas ke haan tey shuda hai magar tum log ho ke shak mein parre hue ho"
6,3,"wohi aik khuda asmano mein bhi hai aur zameen mein bhi, tumahray khulay aur chupay sab haal jaanta hai aur jo buraiee ya bhalai tum kamate ho is se khoob waaqif hai"
6,4,logon ka haal yeh hai ke un ke rab ki nshanyon mein se koi nishani aisi nahi jo un ke samnay aayi ho aur unhon ne is se mun nah mourr liya ho
6,5,"chunancha ab jo haq un ke paas aaya to usay bhi unhon ne jhutla diya acha, jis cheez ka woh ab taq mazaq uratay rahay hain anqareeb is ke mutaliq kuch khabrain inhen pohnchain gi"
6,6,"kya unhon ne dekha nahi ke un se pehlay kitni aisi qomon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain jin ka apne apne zamana mein daur dora raha hai? unn ko hum ne zameen mein woh Iqtidaar bakhsha tha jo tumhe nahi bakhsha hai, un par hum ne aasman se khoob barishain barsaaen aur un ke neechay nhrin baha den, ( magar jab unhon ne kufran Nemat kya to ) aakhir-kaar hum ne un ke gunaaho ki Padaash mein inhen tabah kar diya aur un ki jagah dosray daur ki qomon ko uthaya"
6,7,aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam agar hum tumahray oopar koi kaghaz mein likhi likhai kitaab bhi utaar dete aur log usay apne hathon se chhoo kar bhi dekh letay tab bhi jinhon ne haq ka inkaar kya hai woh yahi kehte ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
6,8,"kehte hain ke is nabi par koi farishta kyun nahi utaara gaya agar kahin hum ne farishta utaar diya hota to ab taq kabhi ka faisla ho chuka hota, phir inhen koi mohlat nah di jati"
